â€œCloud Services = Metadata, optimization, access control, and orchestration layer. Acts like the central brain of Snowflake.â€

How the 3 layers interact
A query comes in â†’ Cloud Services authenticates and optimizes it.
Query is executed â†’ Sent to a Virtual Warehouse (compute).
Virtual Warehouse fetches data â†’ Reads from Database Storage.
Results returned â†’ Cloud Services manage metadata & logging.

